 New Music Video: “Best Thing” – Waje Popular Nigerian singer, Waje has once again proved her vocal dominance with the release of the long-awaited visuals to her latest single, “Best Thing”. Directed by Blessing Uzi and produced by Cracker Milo, the star studded video depicts the importance of appreciating men who are considered to be the less-appreciated gender around the world. The video features stars from the Nigerian entertainment industry such as Noble Igwe, Taymesan, Broda Shaggi and the delectable Nigerian gentleman, Ric Hassani. Watch the video below: 